<div class="com-share" data-id="23942" data-title="《同仁堂也要卖罐装茶饮料了，它能打开这个市场吗？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/23942/medium/23942.jpg?1458063197" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/23942.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
